thread.title: Matt Lloyd
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Matt Lloyd

author: Matt Lloyd
title: Matt Lloyd
text: Great range of products and timely delivery. The Website could have better product information and recommendations. I bought the Scarlett solo DI box, but didn't realise I would have to purchase different audio cables to connect to the speakers I own, meaning I had a another 3 day wait for the cables to arrive before I could use the thing! Everything else about the experience was pretty good though.
